t;在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RhWDcHrS0V-pInwOO-yvuGVvR_51HvoQBhxvXH3gSGpI-uVk_HpePauYRvKw68nUf8qOukVVCZL5Y7RiNCKVrxVdaQ-aSeE5ql-utqjDkk8fRr_gCR8Gu_tiH0F9lwKtkX7hs7Z6hS6p1mDgKU1ARJhw1VbCoGiHSJrhcmdDw8jc1uCnI0J0KuSsbhbeuIQMSo_UuZktYeWAh6T-uEp2F1W898NDrSbljjNpz6ep9s_rVLtgMIBvqesqYjnYrmku7SqZ5TYFO9rSCf5J3LUdrZ0CR-EcZfvtpKtn0I7C0tPUBL56M7P_IZGAv1HVIP6XXZNlW5-9EmSCTUWRhoYCQn9R_O5rh-8S9aS9Lyb52RGo1KW2wzpdYD6sFx0/b_GKd75_DM_fYNyPDB59nZoEKIxWlOTS/18" target="_blank"&gt;降低其投资组合中某些贷款的价值&lt;/a&gt;后，将限制向私人信贷基金提供部分贷款。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;而且情况可能会变得更糟。&lt;/strong&gt;太平洋投资管理公司警告说，该领域&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dD48Y6JnwAbbzuaapLz43yTzWUcH5M3POBabdo14U0EZEiwJz9L8sn0HNh1SPI85_02KcoNZnN0U0ZGDwS4olcU30G4sMnHPI_Y0NreOr-Y_2r_EDnA0qlICkmfnOR3mAZMNfqAJ2ERhWxCa9nzOczEINnQgdHwv_4GjDBSs5yalpo5gufPwipX2B5YFjwQpooZwiUez5KZnCFznlpm-Hezot556HJyJV-llLz354_cLj0-gv8KNo0Hqnkbw_JroryvLTIpQRB9USRdm1Miu_Dyw_Wt6QngdQ9-sWWBWav6hrRIFWEY4Wo2TlBzgLhZ1KZ30U5Z4aIT4cONB-Pn6VCq-m8K9yb6mJgt7yD3PaJyAWAi6uYNjPDIuysw/ayStD-Plz4MODiCwB5OvQZfQZ-h-ycHo/18" target="_blank"&gt;缺乏透明度&lt;/a&gt;意味着，由于一些贷款被标记为零，一些投资者将“急于假设其他一切都一样糟糕”，但事实并非如此。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xsy9ZTg-6uvxiYPavuuEw5NdzsAUm6rvzbmx9agHgoh43rVpgS1cwXcBwyhdmGOFf6MQzd9qh7BNYvzaQKXXPit9YZokJQnBJBbLi9lbPHRcS2wbkDTzl4hlxZC6EDupU9_fcy8vhlEs_SAar-tHToX4E87LabsRhwTgXR4rOiOMhlYHavWRYVYz4IiTFKLTTz50N3oArB9Fe5F3nKq07p9gt1ljbo0uQIlQYxbXHQx_iO2qUc0JrVjwmkRtiR_JV7lX0L_NVoJ2Ivhiny7gDKwL81n-Ur7e2R4Ptd0fvGSPIeyEX3INyxpIIUw1R9yGvlsTCjy-tEN6vw4GjSR2JKueXP3IxIDo1aj9Xgv-6YmeLZh1PufzuINg1Z4/Dw5bEWsT7R3sKrrB3lYOuBpPFWDZKzmk/18" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEzZTKmIbKWk/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGY