; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在伊朗战争引发油价飙升并引发通胀担忧后，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;债券交易员已转向押注&lt;/strong&gt;美国国债损失，大举&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/JJDw7-deBBCUISJxiBxBe5IGW6sPuDHW5TpaHGPNIzRWR_KFP2zCNGe-CvBVl8TgYUlrslLa4Qb_RLYTEs1EjsNrBiOyAAA-R3xQOzTMxlHS92-xfM2rRWTx0VWNVNemqChVagcpT4-eMfRh8MRxLXGUmmLAlsvHazViTmkJ0z6iJEEhkKB80omXrju6SkrQsWmhp_eOAxSbWz0nGyH5w1nj5EROMrhR7Hv0QJHNnUlsS7HST3tkj_drKj1rItH8eP-aRu0ioXHdvt4j0sSd6NG-bkYQ40Gh4QfTUYDiczMl0Yfl7cHcM2Ww8s5E09rBGUTGgCQyAHAjeAxA0dTj2JXVnF6xldbpa6pND3tpE04j1wrZS_BlNdxgHFrr1AHvQeIJtf_KxiWpRSYKRQLpFJQYMMGi_oeNGXe2LcQ1h9M4FO8JAbUKB3xWCwrpFzuphj0J6yJ-lkOATwwAIe-4ShnDuBetUehTa44NjhkD8Ghq97ynEZdiws7t28PFDI3x9JAc8kQ/QA_ITOw5zXyCBmt5eCHY0MUP8FoUK-O-/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着战争的爆发，交易员转而做空美国国债"&gt;抛售看涨期货头寸&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;继美国政府债务&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/QzLLaG7sXARb_AUCk63u2HtkuaDLejkfbEOKLUb2VR_MxyEMQXwUe_-QRAWmDBXZktIi3REn4Zr4xVo6W-cT1sqXhUQcdIj87LiOVMmV4rWQRW_xF6-9xpyNEgfUpioWK9wgeF5Itg9MzIyV4xQXbSCML6aQ5JJF_4tshpP_upK6FmyXaGayMSE-j2wwUcWduKR0XPOKX2Y5cpMGOXaKkMaVE9dxWhKYsjVkLarA9OYIYOrTeTJ0xASLs0anRQGJVemolPAmm1a2KbRv6HaUyPhArgVB2DaN2fHreQBvktVVfCsd2x9pVwGGgMqwJpcCZIg1AmUMqorAclTEGuKr2aNN_UlMV-sLYHXCW3c0LSDdXDh4aNVuy3qbXpAiVPQNhP7xzRIvMlzFj9xktrsqeP3gkAyMMmsck2XrQ9NaImaW1OfVK_yZ7LaZ3yxC4lYQ0t7pUDByf5mBeqStbdeypzexFxslvTSzUcDITDqkVtGRHS5cDLV6R4SKZwX04hVdPJtB/e9VRCptgXGs7PCgil18osg-YmpFG0ts5/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="债券收益率触及 2022 年以来最低水平，限制 2 月涨势"&gt;二月份大幅上涨&lt;/a&gt;之后，上周随着敌对行动的扩大，收益率和原油价格飙升，情绪出现了波动。在周三数据公布之前，交易员还削减了他们预期的美联储今年的政策宽松幅度，预计该数据显示，即使在战斗爆发之前，通胀仍远高于美联储的目标。